'''2018年亚洲公路自行车锦标赛'''是第38届[[亚洲自行车锦标赛|亚洲公路自行车锦标赛]]，于2018年2月8日至12日在缅甸内比都进行。这是缅甸首次主办亚洲公路自行车锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.frontiermyanmar.net/en/myanmar-to-host-asia-cycling-championship-next-month/|title=Myanmar to host Asia Cycling Championship next month|work=Frontier Myanmar|date=2018-01-19|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401193519/https://www.frontiermyanmar.net/en/myanmar-to-host-asia-cycling-championship-next-month/|archivedate=2019-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，共有来自约25个国家和地区的约400名运动员参加精英组、23岁以下组、青年组和残疾组的比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mmtimes.com/news/12-local-cyclists-fray-asian-championships.html|title=12 local cyclists in the fray at Asian championships|publisher=Mynamar Times|date=2018-01-23|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201001033831/https://www.mmtimes.com/news/12-local-cyclists-fray-asian-championships.html|archivedate=2020-10-01}}</ref>。其中精英组共设五个项目<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcf.com.mm/web/Technical%20Guide%202018.pdf|title=2018 ASIAN ROAD & PARA CYCLING CHAMPIONSHIPS Technical Guide|website=mcf.com.mm|date=2018-01-22|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417081248/http://www.mcf.com.mm/web/Technical%20Guide%202018.pdf|archivedate=2018-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

